{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/read-more-button-on-debut-theme-product-page","result":{"pageContext":{"id":593,"date":"2021-03-21T19:13:14","date_gmt":"2021-03-21T19:13:14","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=593"},"modified":"2021-03-21T19:19:58","modified_gmt":"2021-03-21T19:19:58","slug":"read-more-button-on-debut-theme-product-page","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/read-more-button-on-debut-theme-product-page/","title":{"rendered":"&#8220;Read More&#8221; button on Debut theme product page"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Depending on the type of product that you announce, descriptions can get very detailed and subsequently add an obnoxiously large wall of text to your product page. <br><br>A common solution for this type of problem is adding a &#8220;read more&#8221; type of button. In this tutorial I&#8217;ll show you how you can easily achieve that.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/debut-read-more\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a> to download the necessary code files &amp; read about the details of how it works. (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://debut-theme-slider.myshopify.com/collections/hover-images/products/longsleeve-cotton-top\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://debut-theme-slider.myshopify.com/collections/hover-images/products/longsleeve-cotton-top\" target=\"_blank\">Live preview of the end result here</a>).</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Creating the code snippet</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Find the <strong>snippets</strong> folder and, right below it, click on <strong>Add a new snippet</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1918\" height=\"699\" class=\"wp-image-602\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip.png 1918w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-600x219.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-1200x437.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-768x280.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/newsnip-1536x560.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1918px) 100vw, 1918px\" /></li><li>Create a snippet called <strong>ezfy-read-more</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1657\" height=\"806\" class=\"wp-image-604\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create.jpg 1657w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-600x292.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-1200x584.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-768x374.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/create-1536x747.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1657px) 100vw, 1657px\" /></li><li>Inside this new snippet, paste the file that you downloaded and save.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1904\" height=\"879\" class=\"wp-image-606\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1.jpg 1904w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-600x277.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-1200x554.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-768x355.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/save1-1536x709.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1904px) 100vw, 1904px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Adding the code snippet to the product page</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Find the file named <strong>theme.liquid</strong>.</li><li>Inside this file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong></li><li>Paste the following code <strong>before </strong>the <strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong> tag you found:<br><br><pre>{% include 'ezfy-read-more' %}</pre><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1542\" height=\"757\" class=\"wp-image-608\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy.jpg 1542w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-600x295.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-1200x589.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-768x377.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/bdy-1536x754.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1542px) 100vw, 1542px\" /></li><li>Click on save.</li><li>That is it! Now you can visit any product page that has a description&#8217;s height longer than 250px to see how it looks.<br></li></ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Add a &#8220;read more&#8221; button to the description of your product pages.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":595,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,157,82],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-9-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Debut-Slider-Pro-9-100x100.png","post_count":0,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","debut theme","product page"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/593"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:/